TY  - JOUR
AU  - Donohue, John J., III
AU  - Levitt, Steven D.
T1  - Measurement Error, Legalized Abortion, and the Decline in Crime: A Response to Foote and Goetz*
PY  - 2008
Y1  - 2008/02/01
DO  - 10.1162/qjec.2008.123.1.425
JO  - The Quarterly Journal of Economics
JA  - Q J Econ
VL  - 123
IS  - 1
